%main.container.mx-auto.px-4.py-8.max-w-2xl
  %h1.text-3xl.font-bold.mb-6.text-center Rails Upgrade Navigator

  %p.text-gray-600.mb-8.text-center
    GitHubリポジトリのURLを入力すると、gemのバージョン差分を自動解析します。

  = form_with model: @repository, class: 'space-y-4' do |f|
    - if @repository.errors.any?
      .bg-red-100.border.border-red-400.text-red-700.px-4.py-3.rounded.mb-4
        %ul.list-disc.list-inside
          - @repository.errors.full_messages.each do |message|
            %li= message

    .space-y-2
      = f.label :url, 'GitHubリポジトリURL', class: 'block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700'
      = f.text_field :url, placeholder: 'https://github.com/owner/repo', class: 'w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent', required: true

    = f.submit '解析する', class: 'w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors cursor-pointer'

  - if Repository.any?
    .mt-8.text-center
      = link_to '解析履歴を見る', repositories_path, class: 'text-blue-600 hover:underline'
